中转，用了大半年一直很稳，顺便开放给大家用用。</p>\n<p>不是那种赚一波就跑的野鸡站，自己开发团队天天在用，跑路是不可能跑路的。</p>\n<hr/>\n<p><strong>V 友专属：</strong>\n注册就送 <strong>$5 刀**，本帖留 ID 送 **$10 刀</strong>，合计 $15 刀到手直接用。</p>\n<p>充值就是 <strong>1 块钱 = 6 刀</strong>，没有套路，明码标价。</p>\n<p>支持 GPT 5.5 / Claude 4.8 / Gemini 全系，价格自己看：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>0.8 倍 = 0.13 倍率档（日常用足够）</li>\n<li>1.2 倍 = 0.2 倍 倍率档（主力推荐，稳定 速度）</li>\n<li>1.5  =  0.25 倍率档 （优质 不封）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>不限并发，个人小团队都能用，接口兼容 OpenAI 格式，直接改地址就行。</p>\n<hr/>\n<p><strong>邀请返利：</strong>\n朋友用你链接注册充钱，你拿首充 10% + 后续每笔 5%，朋友首充也多拿 10%，双赢。</p>\n<p>就说这么多，好不好用试试就知道，反正是免费送的额度。</p>\n<p>链接：nodeai.click\n注册完记得回来留 ID 给你加额度。</p>\n<p>（别搞小号刷，发现直接 ban ，谢谢配合）</p>\n", "last_modified": 1781347934, "replies": 115, "id": 1220183}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1768280127", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1768280127", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 23583, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3695, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 703436, "username": "sport123", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/sport123", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8553/4395/703436_mini.png?m=1760059769", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8553/4395/703436_normal.png?m=1760059769", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8553/4395/703436_large.png?m=1760059769", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8553/4395/703436_xlarge.png?m=1760059769", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8553/4395/703436_xxlarge.png?m=1760059769", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8553/4395/703436_xxxlarge.png?m=1760059769", "created