n\r\n还是说在编程领域纯 coding 领域模型已经到头了，它可能强在架构设计？还是在其他的领域强？", "content_rendered": "在个人的项目上，我使用 Fable 用了几个小时的 High 模式，然后又把它降到了 Low 模式，反正感觉没有太大的差异啊。<br /><br />还是说在编程领域纯 coding 领域模型已经到头了，它可能强在架构设计？还是在其他的领域强？", "last_modified": 1781340137, "replies": 36, "id": 1220168}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_large.png?m=1747623725", "name": "random", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_normal.png?m=1747623725", "title": "随想", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/random", "topics": 4325, "footer": "", "header": "有的时候，可以停下来找找灵感，然后再继续。", "title_alternative": "Random", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_mini.png?m=1747623725", "stars": 1312, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 59, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 511263, "username": "EyebrowsWhite", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/EyebrowsWhite", "website": "https://eyebrowkang.com", "twitter": "eyebrowkang", "psn": "", "github": "eyebrowkang", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "eyebrowkang", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/530c/66b8/511263_mini.png?m=1754383340", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/530c/66b8/511263_normal.png?m=1754383340", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/530c/66b8/511263_large.png?m=1754383340", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/530c/66b8/511263_xlarge.png?m=1754383340", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/530c/66b8/511263_xxlarge.png?m=1754383340", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/530c/66b8/511263_xxxlarge.png?m=1754383340", "created": 1601955502, "last_modified": 1754383340, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "rtv", "last_touched": 1781407664, "title": "会不会有人为了跟随 AI 的 5 小时重置节奏去尝试多阶段睡眠🤔", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1220217", "created": 1781358820, "deleted": 0, "content": "也叫做达芬奇睡眠\r\n\r\n<https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-cn/多阶段睡眠>", "content_rendered": "<p>也叫做达芬奇睡眠</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-cn/%E5%A4%9A%E9%98%B6