\n<p>简单说说这个 App ，叫 Aion （官网： <a href=\"https://aion.7caifei.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://aion.7caifei.com/</a> ）。</p>\n<p>做它的初衷是嫌市面上的自动退出软件太死板，经常把我挂着的下载或者视频会议给强退了。Aion 做的是“上下文感知退出”：不会傻傻地倒计时，而是会检测你的网络流量、音视频播放，甚至摄像头和麦克风使用状态。如果确定你在开会或下大文件，就先保护起来不退；退出也是走标准 Apple 事件，会提示保存，不至于丢数据。软件完全在本地运行。</p>\n<p>顺便也想请教下各位前辈：大家做 macOS 独立开发，刚起步遇到破解一般怎么调节心态？技术上有没有什么成本低、见效快的防逆向/防破解手段（比如检测运行时签名）？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1781323507, "replies": 26, "id": 1220128}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_large.png?m=1660301119", "name": "create", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_normal.png?m=1660301119", "title": "分享创造", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/create", "topics": 33883, "footer": "", "header": "欢迎你在这里发布自己的最新作品！", "title_alternative": "Create", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1660301119", "stars": 6069, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 17, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 445453, "username": "cpalead", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/cpalead", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e690/8bee/445453_mini.png?m=1711885731", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e690/8bee/445453_normal.png?m=1711885731", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e690/8bee/445453_large.png?m=1711885731", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e690/8bee/445453_xlarge.png?m=1711885731", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e690/8bee/445453_xxlarge.png?m=1711885731", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e690/8bee/445453_xxxlarge.png?m=1711885731", "created": 1570613178, "last_modified": 1711885731, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "18k", "last_touched": 1781368333, "title": "做了一个京东自动保价的插件，留言送一年会员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1220134", "created": 1781326475, "deleted": 0, "content": "地址 https://gitee.com/nnlsm/baojiajingling\r\n